       valid ranges by doing a binary search. This means that the
       driver takes longer to initialize than seems necessary.

       Resetting the scanner does not seem to work. For that rea-
       son, the  driver  sends  a  SCIOCRESTART,  then  uses  any
       remaining  input  until  it  reaches  the  end of the file
       (EOF).

       Not all of the scanners have been identified as flatbed or
       handheld scanners.

       X and Y resolutions are assumed to be the same.

       No  testing  has been done on three-pass or handheld scan-
       ners, or with Automatic Document Feeder support.

